Dia. 01 Really Captured
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par If White carelessly plays the dansu at 1, he is really going to be captured.
\par After Black plays at 2 White has no follow up.
\par
\par Black has three while White has only two liberties.
\par
\par
\par }
