Dia. 02 Correct Answer
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White's dansu from 1 is correct.
\par After Black plays at 2 if White plays the hane at 3, the Black \'a1\'e3 stones are captured.
\par Black can't play dansu from either side.
\par
\par }
