Dia. 04 Pae is Best
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par It is good to play sente with White 1 and then play hane at 3.
\par However Black is going to resist too.
\par
\par After Black 4, Black starts the \cf1\b pae \cf0\b0 with 6. This is the best sequence for both players.
\par
\par If Black plays at A instead of 2, the Black \'a1\'e3 stones are captured without pae.
\par
\par
\par }
